# Root Runnable Build Copy

The runnable GIF Viewer build artifacts were copied from the build output folder to the repository root so the modified viewer can be launched directly from the root folder.

The source tree and original build output folder were left intact.

Copied root-level artifacts:

- GIF Viewer.exe
- GIF Viewer.exe.config
- GIF Viewer.exe.manifest
- GIF Viewer.application
- GifComponents/
- webp_extract_pillow_runtime/
- webp_extract_pillow.exe
